OL,5,Cfines
OL,7,FIt is hoped that new powers given to
OL,8,Fthe council will help tackle anti-
OL,9,Fsocial use of cars, motorised bikes
OL,10,Fand scooters, and the use of vapes in
OL,11,Fplay areas in Sunderland.
OL,13,FSunderland City Council's cabinet of
OL,14,Fsenior councillors agreed to renew and
OL,15,Fexpand powers under the city's Public
OL,16,FSpaces Protection Order (PSPO) at a
OL,17,Fmeeting this week.
