OL,7,FFirst introduced in the city centre in
OL,8,F2017, and extended citywide in 2019,
OL,9,Fthe PSPO gives the council enforcement
OL,10,Fpowers around alcohol control, dog
OL,11,Fcontrol and prohibiting certain
OL,12,Fbehaviour in public spaces.
OL,14,FThe PSPO helps to limit and restrict
OL,15,Factivities which cause nuisance, or
OL,16,Flead to problems for a community,
OL,17,Faccording to a council report.
