OL,7,FIt also gives the council powers to
OL,8,Fissue fixed penalty notices - such as
OL,9,F#100 fine to anyone who doesn't comply
OL,10,Fwith the PSPO measures, which is
OL,11,Freduced to #75 if paid within 10 days.
OL,13,FThose failing to pay could also see
OL,14,Fcourt action resulting in a fine of up
OL,15,Fto #1,000 at the Magistrates Court.
