OL,7,FNew measures proposed as part of the
OL,8,FPSPO renewal would allow the council
OL,9,Fto ban activities linked with 'car
OL,10,Fcruising', which the city council
OL,11,Fstates can put people and properties
OL,12,Fat risk.
OL,14,FProblem activities can range from
OL,15,Fspeeding, racing and performing
OL,16,Fstunts, to sounding horns, playing
OL,17,Floud music, using foul or abusive
OL,18,Flanguage and/or threatening or
OL,19,Fintimidating behaviour, and causing
OL,20,Fobstructions.
